  <brief_title>Comparison of Two Doses of Intranasal Dexmedetomidine as Premedication in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Two Doses of Intranasal Dexmedetomidine as Premedication in Children - a Double-blinded Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
